24:23.819 --> 24:29.347
know there is, but you know that when you leave that 
village, they're going to move back in. And we

24:29.727 --> 24:31.189
lived in that village. They'd help us if we lived in 
the village, but then we would be gone, and we

24:31.229 --> 24:37.138
didn't see Viet Cong at all. We fought straight 
North Vietnamese rebels. We knew they were going

24:40.703 --> 24:46.030
to come back and live in that village, so they were 
more afraid of them than they were of us.

