39:08.333 --> 39:13.663
at me? I went to defend the United States, and 
you're taking it out on me, and I didn't, you know. I

39:20.337 --> 39:21.158
didn't shoot you. I didn't shoot at you. Why are you 
getting that at me for? And that's how a lot of us, we

39:23.081 --> 39:26.025
felt very frustrated and very angry. Of course, 
the sweetheart of sweethearts today is Jane

