42:03.782 --> 42:09.469
ideas are not always right. But they might not be 
wrong either. It's just someone else has a

42:10.851 --> 42:12.593
different idea. I grew up a lot. Being honest, I 
kind of, if of course I don't have a son, I've got a

42:14.436 --> 42:18.201
daughter. And I've always said that if I had to do it 
all over again, or not all over again, if I had a son,

