42:40.252 --> 42:44.922
OK, Dad, I want to go to a college, he'd have to enter 
one with a core. He has to learn. to grow up, but I

42:46.870 --> 42:50.775
believe the military does help. Some people 
don't, but it did me, and I'm very happy that they

42:50.835 --> 42:56.843
did that for me. It also paid for my education. It 
taught me how to lie and get away with it. Did you

43:03.152 --> 43:15.308
find while you were there that you grew more 
